OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Presenter Nicky Campbell said he wept  
OL,6, in his wife's arms after a sheriff     
OL,7, found a private school teacher abused  
OL,8, him and others over a 20-year period.  
OL,10,FJohn Brownlee beat students at         
OL,11,FEdinburgh Academy with wooden bats and 
OL,12,Fpushed one boy down a flight of stairs 
OL,13,Fduring a campaign of physical violence.
OL,15,FVictims described the teacher, now 89, 
OL,16,Fas a "psychopath" and a "sadist".      
OL,18,FAn examination of facts hearing        
OL,19,Fconcluded earlier after he was deemed  
OL,20,Fmedically unfit to stand trial.        
